Article 26 is about two universal workplace experiences,

00:00:03.737 --> 00:00:06.239
promotion and advancement.

00:00:06.306 --> 00:00:08.842
This Article explains merit promotion policies and

00:00:08.908 --> 00:00:13.146
procedures for Title 5 Bargaining Unit Employees.

00:00:13.213 --> 00:00:16.750
Article 26 covers a range of methods to advance or promote

00:00:16.816 --> 00:00:19.686
Employees based on their qualifications,

00:00:19.753 --> 00:00:23.456
including career ladders, promotions, and appointments.


